|YKODarkwind's calendar is based on a 300 day year, Each Day is
approximately 20 hours, and 1 week is a ten-day long.  There
are 3 ten-day in a month (or 30 days), and 10 months in a
year.  There are three moons that orbit high above Geshtei
all of which are distinctly diferentiable because of their
colors.  The largest is Dailos, also known as the Magenta moon.
The next largest is Markas, the Red moon, and the smallest,
Tekal, is called the Green moon.
 
